Title: title: 'This week in Nushell #305'
Path: Nushell
Content:
@sholderbach:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16054] bumped 
``strip-ansi-escapes``
 to deduplicate 
``vte``
 (#16054)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16052] added 
``tango``
 folder to .gitignore (#16052)
@Axlefublr:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16051] added note for figuring out datetime escape sequences to default config (#16051)
@musicinmybrain:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16045] updated which from 7.0.3 to 8.0.0 (#16045)
@fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16044] updated nushell to latest reedline e4221b9 (#16044)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16012] fixed LS_COLORS fi=0 coloring (#16012)
@adithyaov:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16033] updated how paths are interpreted in 
``start``
 (#16033)
@Tyarel8:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16032] added 
``is_const``
 information to std/help (#16032)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16019] fixed windows 
``--help``
 output collection for gui programs in std/help (#16019)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15962] added 
``--help``
 support for external commands (#15962)
@ayax79:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16031] upgraded to polars 0.49 (#16031)
@Bahex:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16021] fixed hooks to correctly update config state when changing 
``$env.config``
 (#16021)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16016] preserved round float numbers' type in 
``to <format>``
 (#16016)
@hustcer:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16020] added loongarch64-unknown-linux-musl build target (#16020)
@Mrfiregem:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16018] allowed 
``update cells``
 to work on single records (#16018)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15955] streamed lazy 
``default``
 output (#15955)
@132ikl:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16015] added 
``only``
 command to 
``std-rfc/iter``
 (#16015)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15892] added backtick code formatting to 
``help``
 (#15892)
@echasnovski:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16013] added 'double' table mode (#16013)
@kumarUjjawal:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/16001] fixed 
``random dice``
 to gracefully handle --sides 0 using NonZeroUsize (#16001)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15897] made drop nth command support spreadable arguments (#15897)
@blindFS:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15998] fixed completion for external path arguments with spaces (#15998)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15780] improved scalability of get_columns (#15780)
